verses.text: \w A|strong="H0369"\w* psalm \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w*. \w He|strong="H0430"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* walketh without blemish, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* worketh justice:

\w He|strong="H6213"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* speaketh truth \w in|strong="H1571"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* heart, \w who|strong="H3605"\w* hath \w not|strong="H0369"\w* \w used|strong="H6213"\w* deceit \w in|strong="H1571"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* tongue: \w Nor|strong="H0369"\w* hath \w done|strong="H6213"\w* evil \w to|strong="H0369"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* neighbour: \w nor|strong="H0369"\w* \w taken|strong="H5493"\w* \w up|strong="H3605"\w* \w a|strong="H0259"\w* reproach \w against|strong="H1571"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* neighbours.

\w In|strong="H3068"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* sight \w the|strong="H3605"\w* malignant \w is|strong="H3068"\w* brought \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w nothing|strong="H3808"\w*: \w but|strong="H3808"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* glorifieth \w them|strong="H7121"\w* \w that|strong="H3045"\w* fear \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w*. \w He|strong="H3068"\w* \w that|strong="H3045"\w* sweareth \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* neighbour, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* deceiveth \w not|strong="H3808"\w*;

\w He|strong="H3588"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* hath \w not|strong="H3588"\w* put \w out|strong="H8033"\w* \w his|strong="H3588"\w* money \w to|strong="H0430"\w* usury, \w nor|strong="H1755"\w* taken bribes against \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w innocent|strong="H6662"\w*: \w He|strong="H3588"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* doth these things \w shall|strong="H1755"\w* \w not|strong="H3588"\w* \w be|strong="H0430"\w* moved \w for|strong="H3588"\w* ever.
